title: The Railway Children (2000) TV
description:
I've changed my mind. Instead of uploading all the remaining movies I had planned to create subtitles for, I've decided to cancel or put that off. 

This Masterpiece Theatre TV movie is a favorite in our household. It's not only a children's show. 

As usual there are two text files, one for commentary, the other for closed captions.

This submission is dedicated to someone in Bucharest, Romania.
I hope you enjoy it.
